%F A090281 a(n) = (floor(-abs(n-(16*ceiling(n/8)-7)/2) + (16*ceiling(n/8)-7)/2)) mod 8. - _Wesley Ivan Hurt_, Mar 26 2014
%F A090281 G.f.: -x*(x^4+x^3+x^2+x+1) / ((x-1)*(x^4+1)). - _Colin Barker_, Mar 26 2014
